data.description: Very clean, well maintained unit. Original owner. No pets, no smoke. Main ensuite with amazing closet space. Similar space in lower level! Laundry up & down. On demand water heater. Newer HVAC system and thermostat.. Huge fenced private patio w/Wasatch view. Quiet well run community ,nicely landscaped with many trees. Sunny, bright kitchen. Large dining room. Storage galore! Oversize garage w/cabinets. Friendly community, (not just seniors). On site manager.
